        <item>
            <title>Nikon Z50 II 瞄准入门创作者，配备专用色彩方案切换按钮</title>
            <description>&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;Nikon Z50 II 瞄准入门创作者，配备专用色彩方案切换按钮&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-11/19905e90-9d24-11ef-a6fb-59e7e1c5e60f&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;link &quot; href=&quot;https://tw.news.yahoo.com/tag/Nikon&quot; data-i13n=&quot;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:Nikon;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0&quot;&gt;Nikon&lt;/a&gt; Z50 II 瞄准入门创作者，配备专用色彩方案切换按钮&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;Nikon 早些时候推出了入门无反新机 Z50 II，相比 5 年前的 Z50 它在拍摄速度、对焦、录影等方面均有改进，不过最大的卖点是支援自订、下载不同的色彩方案。用户可根据自己的喜好调整色彩、亮度、对比度并将其保存为专属风格，或是免费下载由 Nikon 推荐、知名创作者制作的成品方案。在机身上你还能找到一颗专门的「最佳化校准」按钮，方便用户快速切换方案以「享受更换胶片或滤镜般的多样化影像表达乐趣」。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-iframe-wrapper&quot; data-embed-anchor=&quot;ad63a722-8089-5bf0-b8f0-2d4d54038931&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/h6vBVsneYU0&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allow=&quot;encrypted-media; picture-in-picture; web-share&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;规格方面，Z50 II 搭载了 20.9MP 感光器和 Z9 同款的 EXPEED 7 影像处理器，支援 9 种对象侦测，自动对焦速度较前代也有提升。其电子快门连拍速度可达到 30fps（JPEG），使用机械快门则为 11fps（JPEG/RAW）。装置可录制 4K 30p（无裁切）或 4K 60p（1.5 倍裁切）影片，并且支援 N-Log 10-bit 拍摄。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container caas-img-loader&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img caas-lazy has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;Nikon Z50 II&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-11/4d3001b0-9d24-11ef-a79d-eccda2deb055&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;Nikon Z50 II&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;这款产品配备了内置闪光灯、翻转萤幕和 1,000 尼特亮度的 236 万点 EVF，并提供了单 UHS-II 卡槽、麦克风/耳机插孔和 USB-C 埠。它含卡、电的总重量约为 550g，续航力差不多是 300 张照片。比较遗憾的是，这款相机本身并不具备防震机能。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container caas-img-loader&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img caas-lazy has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;Nikon Z50 II&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-11/62e541f0-9d24-11ef-bbfa-f4be221d86a4&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;Nikon Z50 II&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;Nikon Z50 II 的机身价格为 US$910，含 Nikkor Z 16-50mm f/3.5-5.6 VR 镜头的组合价为 US$1,050。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;紧贴最新科技资讯、网购优惠，追随 Yahoo Tech 各大社交平台！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech Facebook：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:1;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech Instagram：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:2;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 社群：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:3;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 频道：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:4;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;🎉📱 Tech Telegram 频道：&lt;a data-i13n=&quot;cpos:5;pos:1&quot; href=&quot;https://t.me/yahootechhk&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://t.me/yahootechhk;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://t.me/yahootechhk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
